'''Truffle Oil''' is an [[Artisan Goods|Artisan Good]] made in the [[Oil Maker]] from a [[Truffle]]. It takes 6 hours to produce. Despite being listed as "A gourmet cooking ingredient" there are no cooking recipes that use it, but it is used to make the [[Rain Totem]].

